            <abstract>
                <p>The so-called school chants form part of the <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3186Meeraf">Mǝʿrāf</ref>, and are also attested as an independent collection.
               The text parts composing them might vary; further study is needed on the manuscript circulation of this collection.
                </p>
